Good catch Sarah.

Fixed backend to match your approach:

```javascript
const durationHours = (endDate - startDate) / (1000 * 60 * 60);
if (durationHours > 18) {
    // Force non-repeating
}
```

Examples:
- Weekly milonga 8pm-1am (5 hours) → NOT multi-day ✓
- Festival Fri 7pm - Sun 10pm (51 hours) → multi-day ✓

